This project requires AndEngine in the Eclipse workspace. Please follow these steps to add it:

1. Add "https://github.com/nicolasgramlich/AndEngine.git" to your git repositories and checkout the "GLES2" branch.

2. Right click the added repo in the "Git Repositories" view and select "Import projects...".

3. Select "Import existing projects", click next and confirm by click on finish.

4. Right click the Tamagotchi project in the workspace, select "Properties" and select "Android" from the list on the left.

5. Make sure that AndEngine is displayed (like in this screenshot: http://i.imgur.com/FzKci.png)

6. All done. Have fun coding